@Jebman82  Thanks for the update. Everything is working here on my end. I don't use <abbr title="Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)">FAR</abbr> but in-flight the symmetry works for me.

Also you mentioned something about holding M1 and M2 for finer increments, but that doesn't work for me since I use WASD Camera mod. However, holding M2 only works ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif ":)") It's a bit finnick but does the job.

I'll be using this fork for a while.
